{
  "stem": "15577.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And with the time-- it's a very interesting chapter of our life, because with the time, we got so friendly with these Germans that we are listening-- I am jumping.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After half a year or something of-- first of all, we were mixing the-- in the whole flat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sleeping in my room, after a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were going around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It means we didn't go to their bedroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their bedroom was established in my sister's room, which was my sister's room before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were, very often, sitting in the dining room all together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got so friendly that-- I don't remember, but we-- we came, even, to such a point that we were listening to English radio together, which was something outstanding, and-- and really rare.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I jump again, in my story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This man, some-- I don't know if-- how-- how he changed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He changed so much that he-- with time, the persecution of Jews went on and on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he came to my father, and--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And asked him to let me-- he wanted to take me to Turkey, to get me out, because I-- I was a young-- the young one, so he wanted to take me out of Poland, to bring me to Turkey.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I can go wherever I want.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not accepted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By all of us-- first of all, we didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The secondly, we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Second-- and thirdly, don't forget, Jews were always hoping it's last month, or the last week, or the last day of the-- but a fact is that we came to such relations that he could speak about it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at the end, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was maybe after a year.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
